  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>the\n        horses</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>There are two possible interpretations:\n        the horses may be drawing Phoebus' chariot, but they may\n        also be beating up the dawn on earth, with the sun rising\n        overhead. Hence they would represent the army approaching\n        from Istria, converging Venice's fall to Austria with\n        Antony's fall to Ceasar.</font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>The War</td>\n<td><a href=\"Portrait175_JJ.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Istria_H.htm\">Istria in Herod</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sir Ferdinand Klein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "the horses There are two possible interpretations: the horses may be drawing Phoebus' chariot, but they may also be beating up the dawn on earth, with the sun rising overhead. Hence they would represent the army approaching from Istria, converging Venice's fall to Austria with Antony's fall to Ceasar. reference topics The War Istria in Herod Sir Ferdinand Klein back to \"Burbank\"",
